[Student "S"]
{You dealt this hand.  

Nice hand. 19 points and a good 5-card Major. You open 1\H. Partner responds 2\H. What is your next bid? 

You revalue to 20 points (doubleton \S) and partner has between 6 and 10. So, 26 to 30 is the total. Game should be there, but slam is out of reach. So you bid 4\H.}

